flowchart TD
    Start([👤 用户请求]) --> Analyze[🔎 分析用户意图]
    Analyze --> Route{🎯 判断请求类型}

    Route -->|流程 / 业务逻辑| Activity[📋 Activity Diagram Guide]
    Route -->|部署 / 云 / K8s| Deploy[☁️ Deployment Diagram Guide]
    Route -->|架构 / 组件| Arch[🏗️ Architecture Diagram Guide]
    Route -->|API / 交互流程| Sequence[🔁 Sequence Diagram Guide]
    Route -->|代码转图| CodeToDiagram[🧩 Code-to-Diagram Guide]
    Route -->|设计文档| DesignDoc[📄 Design Document Template]
    Route -->|Unicode / 图标| Unicode[✨ Unicode Symbols Guide]
    Route -->|提取 / 校验 / 转图片| Scripts[🐍 Python Scripts]

    Activity --> LoadGuide[📚 按需读取专用指南]
    Deploy --> LoadGuide
    Arch --> LoadGuide
    Sequence --> LoadGuide
    CodeToDiagram --> LoadGuide
    DesignDoc --> LoadGuide
    Unicode --> LoadGuide

    Scripts --> Execute[⚙️ 执行脚本工具]

    LoadGuide --> Generate[🧠 生成 Mermaid 图或文档]
    Generate --> Style[🎨 添加 Unicode 语义符号和高对比样式]

    Style --> NeedExport{🛡️ 需要保存 / 转图片 / 写入文档?}

    NeedExport -->|否| Output[📤 直接输出 Mermaid 代码]
    NeedExport -->|是| SaveMmd[💾 保存 .mmd 文件]

    SaveMmd --> Validate{✅ Mermaid 校验通过?}

    Validate -->|是| Render[🖼️ 生成 PNG / SVG]
    Render --> AddMarkdown[📝 可选加入 Markdown 引用]
    AddMarkdown --> Output

    Validate -->|否| Troubleshoot[🔧 查 troubleshooting guide]
    Troubleshoot --> Fix{🧩 找到修复方案?}

    Fix -->|是| Generate
    Fix -->|否| ExternalSearch[🌐 外部搜索 / 其他工具辅助]
    ExternalSearch --> Generate

    Execute --> Output
    Output --> Done([✅ 交付结果])

    classDef start fill:#90EE90,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:darkgreen
    classDef process fill:#87CEEB,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:darkblue
    classDef decision fill:#FFD700,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:black
    classDef guide fill:#E6E6FA,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:darkblue
    classDef script fill:#FFE4B5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#8B4513
    classDef error fill:#FFB6C1,stroke:#DC143C,stroke-width:2px,color:black
    classDef output fill:#98FB98,stroke:#228B22,stroke-width:2px,color:darkgreen

    class Start,Done start
    class Analyze,LoadGuide,Generate,Style,SaveMmd,Render,AddMarkdown,ExternalSearch process
    class Route,NeedExport,Validate,Fix decision
    class Activity,Deploy,Arch,Sequence,CodeToDiagram,DesignDoc,Unicode guide
    class Scripts,Execute script
    class Troubleshoot error
    class Output output
